note:
Every relationship I've ever tried at has failed. It's because I don't really know how to function or keep someone happy.. because I'm so strange. I almost feel like I'm going through the motions, trying to blend in with everyone around me. The irony is that I'm gifted at social engineering, guessing what people might do.. but online. In real life I couldn't be more clueless.

The more I hack, the deeper I dive, the more knowledge I gain, the more I learn about people, the more alone I feel.
